article_title: Wall To Rapid City Open On I-90
article_text:
Pierre, SD

The section of Interstate 90 between Wall and Rapid City is now open. I-90 is now open from the Minnesota border to Sturgis. Crews continue to work on the stretch of Sturgis to the Wyoming border.

Crews were delayed by drifts and stray cattle between Wall and Rapid City. Drivers are warned that with fences buried, there could be stray cattle on the roads.
